Day 55: Kubernetes Sidecar Containers

Date: October 24, 2025
Overview
Implemented sidecar pattern for logging and monitoring.
Key Concepts Learned

Sidecar pattern
Multi-container pods
Container communication
Log aggregation

Commands Used
yamlspec:
  containers:
  - name: main-app
    image: app:latest
  - name: log-sidecar
    image: fluentd:latest
Challenges Faced
Container startup order and ensuring sidecars were ready before main container.
